items.title: Tata Power awards contracts worth Rs 11,481 crore to local suppliers
items.description: The joint ventures between Tata Power and the Odisha government, placed orders worth Rs 8,690 crore with local MSMEs and Rs 2,791 crore to non-MSMEs by the Discoms over the past three years since taking over the state's power distribution operations
